cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.SY

The paper focuses on using neural networks for long-term prediction of mechanical phenomena based on sensory data, which falls under the domain of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of sensory data suggests the involvement of computer vision (cs.CV) techniques. The prediction of mechanical phenomena also involves robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY).
